#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Move</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Undo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Déplacer</guimenu><guimenuitem>Annuler</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Removes your last move</action> as well as the computer's last move "
"from the board."
msgstr ""
"<action>Annule votre dernier coup</action> ainsi que celui de l'ordinateur "
"du plateau."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:268
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>H</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Move</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Hint</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>H</keycap></shortcut><guimenu>Déplacer</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Conseil</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:270
#, no-c-format
msgid "The computer will <action>provide a hint for your next move.</action>"
msgstr ""
"L'ordinateur vous <action>fournira un conseil pour votre prochain coup.</"
"action>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Last Move</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Vue</guimenu><guimenuitem>Afficher le dernier coup</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid "Highlights your opponent's last move."
msgstr "Surligner le dernier mouvement de votre adversaire."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Legal Moves</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Vue</guimenu><guimenuitem>Afficher les coups autorisés</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Highlights all the moves available</action> for your current move."
msgstr ""
"<action>Surligne tous les mouvements disponibles</action> pour votre coup "
"actuel."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Move History</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Vue</guimenu><guimenuitem>Afficher l'historique des coups</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:285
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enables/Disables the move history sidebar."
msgstr "Active ou désactive la barre d'historique des mouvements."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Animation Speed</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Configuration</guimenu><guisubmenu>Vitesse d'animation</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>A submenu to set the game animation speed</action> between "
"<guimenuitem>Slow</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Normal</guimenuitem>, and "
"<guimenuitem>Fast</guimenuitem> options."
msgstr ""
"<action>Un sous-menu pour définir la vitesse d'animation du jeu</action> "
"parmi les options <guimenuitem>Lent</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Normal</"
"guimenuitem> et <guimenuitem>Rapide</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Use Colored Chips</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Configuration</guimenu><guimenuitem>Utiliser les jetons colorés</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:295
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Toggle the color of the stones between black and white (default),</"
"action> and red and blue."
msgstr ""
"<action>Basculer la couleur des jetons entre le noir et le blanc (défaut)</"
"action> et le rouge et le bleu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Difficulty</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Configuration</guimenu><guisubmenu>Difficulté</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Set the difficulty</action> from <guimenuitem>Very Easy</"
"guimenuitem> to <guimenuitem>Impossible</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"<action>Définir la difficulté</action> à partir de <guimenuitem>Très facile</"
"guimenuitem> à <guimenuitem>Impossible</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &kreversi; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> and "
"<guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the sections "
"about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"De plus, &kreversi; possède des éléments communs de menu &kde; "
"<guimenu>Configuration</guimenu> et <guimenu>Aide</guimenu>. Pour plus "
"d'informations, veuillez consulter les sections <ulink url=\"help:/"
"fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">Menu de configuration</ulink> et "
"<ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-help\">Menu d'aide</ulink> "
"des fondamentaux de &kde;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently asked questions"
msgstr "Foire aux questions"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:318
#, no-c-format
msgid "I want to change the way this game looks. Can I?"
msgstr "Je veux modifier la façon dont le jeu s'affiche. Est-ce possible ?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:319
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The only part of the game that can be changed is the color of the stones. To "
"change the color of the stones use the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Use Colored Chips</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Le seul élément du jeu qui peut être modifié est la couleur des jetons. Pour "
"cela, veuillez utiliser l'élément de menu <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Configuration</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Utiliser les jetons colorés</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> sur la barre de menu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use the keyboard to play the game?"
msgstr "Puis-je utiliser le clavier pour jouer à ce jeu ?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:323
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. &kreversi; does not provide for the keyboard play."
msgstr "Non. &kreversi; ne fournit aucun moyen de jouer avec le clavier."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:326
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I have to quit the game now, but I am not finished yet. Can I save my "
"progress?"
msgstr ""
"Je veux quitter le jeu maintenant, mais ma partie n'est pas terminée. Puis "
"je l'enregistrer ?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. &kreversi; does not have a <quote>Save</quote> feature."
msgstr ""
"Non. &kreversi; ne possède aucune fonctionnalité <quote>Enregistrer</quote>."

